          %h3 "Debuggers"
          %ul
            %li Debuggers are a Swiss Army Knife.
            %li Allow us to set "breakpoints" in code that will pause a running program.
            %li When a breakpoint statement or mark is hit we can then examine the current state of the program.
            %li
              In Ruby/Rails is provided by the
              %code debugger
              gem in Ruby versions < 2.0 and the
              %code byebug
              gem in Ruby versions >= 2.0

